project.name: Hero: Molly Tuttle: From Rancid Covers to Grammy Gold

data.label: Style
data.name: w33s3 Dark
data.description: Dark, moody atmosphere with high contrast lighting. Cinematic composition with neon accent colors against deep blacks. Professional photography feel, dramatic shadows, rich color depth. Modern minimalist aesthetic, no text or watermarks.

data.label: Action
data.content: Noir comic book style illustration, muted blacks and grays with selective pops of amber and green. A woman's hands flatpicking an acoustic guitar with intensity. Split composition: warm amber glow on one side (bluegrass), electric green on the other (punk). Heavy ink lines, dramatic shadows, graphic novel aesthetic. Focus on the guitar and hands, no face. Film grain texture.
